{"tid":1058714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"ATM存錢！後方男持刀搶走1萬…瞄一眼「戶頭餘額」冷笑秒還她","createTime":"2019-03-12T17:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T01:55:40.000Z","uid":7232,"like":47,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6a7bc65e500953859319c4ad0f149da02ca5b26c","tid":1058714,"uid":7232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T17:07:08.000Z","msg":"廣東省河源市近日發生一起好氣又好笑的搶劫案，一名李姓女子在ATM存款時，被後方突然出現的男子持刀搶劫，她隨即交出手中的2500元人民幣（約新台幣1.1萬元），不過男子似乎不甘心只拿到這點錢，便要求查看李女戶頭還剩多少，沒想到畫面顯示「沒有餘額」，搶匪竟心生憐憫把錢全數歸還，冷笑轉頭離去。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3949/3949861.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3949%2F3949861.jpg&h=b4d51cf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n綜合陸媒報導，李女表示，她在存款時就看到男子在銀行門口徘徊，一轉身就被對方持刀靠近，她嚇得尖叫，隨即意識到男子要搶劫，便趕緊說「錢可以給你，但不要傷害我」；不料，李女交出2500元人民幣（約新台幣1.1萬元）後，男子還要她出示戶頭餘額。<br />\n<br />\n李女聽從要求操作給搶匪看，畫面跳出「沒有餘額」後，對方就將錢全數歸還，還露齒冷笑離開。雖然搶匪「良心發現」把錢還給受害人，但是他的行為仍構成犯罪，警方在事後根據監視器畫面逮捕嫌犯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3949/3949860.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3949%2F3949860.jpg&h=787f1c66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網友看完紛紛表示，「搶匪真的是發自內心的嘲笑」、「事實證明，沒錢連搶匪都看不起你」、「還回來就算了，你笑就太過分了！」、「犯了法就該得到應有的懲處」、「女子心裡一定滿滿問號」、「搶匪：嘖，真窮」、「還好我一直很安全！」"},{"pid":"29ae01a68c68ff7e9ec3d703461999f5981cc0d3","tid":1058714,"uid":105795,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T17:15:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3949/3949860.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3949%2F3949860.jpg&h=787f1c66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20ae113a88673726989c958ee229f74c3d34030b","tid":1058714,"uid":47663,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T17:15:43.000Z","msg":"條女好似幾靚"},{"pid":"6c471edee3f60b7ebfab7fcf805dc9ac99b3a65e","tid":1058714,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T17:48:36.000Z","msg":"恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4121df25ccea73e5beda4621102364c1e5f1a21d","tid":1058714,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29ae01a68c68ff7e9ec3d703461999f5981cc0d3","tid":1058714,"uid":105795,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T17:15:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3949/3949860.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3949%2F3949860.jpg&h=787f1c66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T17:51:27.000Z","msg":"屌乜撚丫，條友笑完頭也不回，條女應該又窮又醜，所以先比返2500佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8083e70c58b4b6094087e4e7c0e08664023430e4","tid":1058714,"uid":75050,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T17:55:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bZqKZmm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbZqKZmm.png&h=7437303d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a536875061208505e9969e1e8ded3a1ea3d41793","tid":1058714,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T17:58:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"827fa03c91c1f1a35b18e13f37b5cf123ab5ff57","tid":1058714,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T18:03:30.000Z","msg":"有畫面"},{"pid":"33854c0a3ce2017b6d2dba1638f11279f17bd65d","tid":1058714,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T18:04:35.000Z","msg":"盗亦有道 點解唔劫色？"},{"pid":"d4ad10bc8ef09a646f3a15d78e22f95825d48f3c","tid":1058714,"uid":49245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33854c0a3ce2017b6d2dba1638f11279f17